Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:09.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961,65.714)}{\c&HCF87DF&}我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961,65.714)}{\c&HCF87DF&}這份心意是如此真誠
